---
title: Cheesy Chicken Empanadas with Charred Corn Salsa
description: We've taken the best of an empanada; flavourful cheesy chicken in a transcendent pastry! Our pre-rolled puff pastry is easy to use with a simple fill, gather, pinch and bake technique. Served with sweet and crunchy corn and bell pepper salsa, we've got dinner covered!
